            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[
## What's Changed

- Updated the Sentra installer background and production update copy so release surfaces no longer show old product branding.
- Cleaned the About panel to show a simple version/build line while preserving full release provenance in diagnostics.
- Fixed the Tools management view so available tool counts map to visible tool rows.
- Refreshed visible Sentra branding for built-in themes, CLI setup copy, onboarding strings, and primary plugin catalog cards.
]]></description>
